     fhir:Narrative.status [ fhir:value "extensions" ] ;
     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xml:lang=\"fr-FR\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" lang=\"fr-FR\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Narratif généré : EnsembleValeurs jdv-quantite-exposition-rayonnements-cisis</b></p><a name=\"jdv-quantite-exposition-rayonnements-cisis\"> </a><a name=\"hcjdv-quantite-exposition-rayonnements-cisis\"> </a><div style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: #d9e0e7; padding: 6px; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid #8da1b4; border-radius: 5px; line-height: 60%\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px\">version : 10; Dernière mise à jour : 2026-06-22 13:59:49+0200; Langue : fr-FR</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px\">Profil: <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/shareablevalueset.html\">Shareable ValueSet</a></p></div><ul><li>Include ce(s) code(s) tel qu'il(s) est (sont) défini(s) dans <a href=\"http://dicom.nema.org/resources/ontology/DCM\"><code>http://dicom.nema.org/resources/ontology/DCM</code></a><span title=\"La version est explicitement indiquée comme étant 01\"> version ?01</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Affichage</b></td><td><b>Définition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-111636\">111636</a></td><td>Dose dans l'air à l'entrée du patient (Kerma dans l'air)</td><td>Exposure measurement in air at the reference point that does not include back scatter, according to MQCM 1999</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-111637\">111637</a></td><td>DGM total : Dose Glandulaire Moyenne Total</td><td>Average Glandular Dose to a single breast accumulated over multiple images</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-113722\">113722</a></td><td>PDS Total : Produit Dose Surface Total</td><td>Total calculated Dose Area Product (in the scope of the including report)</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-113726\">113726</a></td><td>PDS de Scopie Total : Produit Dose Surface de Scopie Total</td><td>Total calculated Dose Area Product applied in Fluoroscopy Modes (in the scope of the including report)</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-113727\">113727</a></td><td>PDS de Graphie Total : Produit Dose Surface de Graphie Total</td><td>Total calculated Dose Area Product applied in Acquisition Modes (in the scope of the including report)</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-113730\">113730</a></td><td>Temps total de scopie</td><td>Total accumulated clock time of Fluoroscopy in the scope of the including report (i.e., the sum of the Irradiation Duration values for accumulated fluoroscopy irradiation events)</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-113731\">113731</a></td><td>Nombre total d’images radiographiques</td><td>Accumulated Count of exposure pulses (single or multi-frame encoded) created from irradiation events performed with high dose (acquisition)</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-113507\">113507</a></td><td>Activité administrée</td><td>The calculated activity at the Radiopharmaceutical Start Time when the radiopharmaceutical is administered to the patient. The residual activity (i.e. radiopharmaceutical not administered) , if measured, is reflected in the calculated value. The estimated extravasation is not reflected in the calculated value</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-113813\">113813</a></td><td>PDL Total : Produit Dose Longueur Total</td><td>The total dose length product defined scope of accumulation</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-113830\">113830</a></td><td>IDSV Moyen : Indice de Dose Scanographique Volumique</td><td>\"Mean CTDIvol\" refers to the average value of the CTDIvol associated with this acquisition</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-113839\">113839</a></td><td>E : Dose efficace</td><td>Effective dose in mSv</td></tr></table></li></ul></div>"
  ] ;
